1
00:00:09,013 --> 00:00:09,775
<i>C'mon!</i>

2
00:00:16,354 --> 00:00:18,914
<i>Running like a fugitive,</i>

3
00:00:20,057 --> 00:00:22,116
<i>Being chased by something</i>

4
00:00:23,794 --> 00:00:26,456
<i>Inside my heart is pounding</i>

5
00:00:27,798 --> 00:00:30,426
<i>My throat dry like it's withering</i>

6
00:00:32,069 --> 00:00:35,163
<i>For no single one,</i>

7
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:38,900
<i>To none does belong,</i>

8
00:00:40,244 --> 00:00:44,510
<i>This time is ours, right now...</i>

9
00:00:47,285 --> 00:00:49,150
<i>Unraveling the pain,</i>

10
00:00:49,253 --> 00:00:50,982
<i>Unraveling our hearts,</i>

11
00:00:51,055 --> 00:00:53,387
<i>Unraveling shadows</i>

12
00:00:54,926 --> 00:00:56,689
<i>Stifling our breath,</i>

13
00:00:56,761 --> 00:00:58,661
<i>Reaching for beyond,</i>

14
00:00:58,729 --> 00:01:01,163
<i>Tearing through the dark</i>

15
00:01:03,067 --> 00:01:09,631
<i>In fighting and in love</i>

16
00:01:10,608 --> 00:01:13,236
<i>To the distant light above,</i>

17
00:01:13,911 --> 00:01:16,880
<i>Yes, we are on the way</i>

18
00:01:21,686 --> 00:01:22,914
<i>I wanna rock...</i>

19
00:01:25,489 --> 00:01:27,013
<i>Rockin' my heart</i>

20
00:01:31,590 --> 00:01:32,488
Die.

21
00:01:34,927 --> 00:01:36,394
Darn!

22
00:01:36,695 --> 00:01:38,287
Shadow Clone Jutsu!

23
00:01:42,334 --> 00:01:47,294
Hmm... Shadow Clone Jutsu.
And there are quite a few of them.

24
00:02:11,029 --> 00:02:12,121
Here I go!

25
00:02:31,901 --> 00:02:32,993
It's impossible, after all...

26
00:02:33,986 --> 00:02:36,284
There is no way that
you can beat a guy!

27
00:02:40,459 --> 00:02:43,553
<i>There is only one way left</i>
<i>to defeat this guy.</i>

28
00:02:44,329 --> 00:02:45,261
Sasuke!

29
00:02:49,835 --> 00:02:50,426
<i>I see!</i>

30
00:02:50,636 --> 00:02:52,297
<i>So that's your plan, Naruto!</i>

31
00:02:52,871 --> 00:02:54,168
<i>That's pretty good for you!</i>

32
00:03:09,588 --> 00:03:10,850
Demon Wind Shuriken,

33
00:03:11,290 --> 00:03:12,279
Windmill of Shadows...

34
00:03:21,333 --> 00:03:24,359
A Shuriken won't work on me.

35
00:03:39,685 --> 00:03:40,652
I see.

36
00:03:41,620 --> 00:03:44,248
This time it's aiming for my real body...

37
00:03:45,557 --> 00:03:46,353
But...

38
00:03:46,792 --> 00:03:47,622
It's not so easy!

39
00:03:51,530 --> 00:03:53,691
<i>A Shuriken in the Shuriken's shadow!</i>

40
00:03:54,099 --> 00:03:54,793
<i>This is...</i>

41
00:03:55,434 --> 00:03:56,867
<i>The Shadow Shuriken Jutsu!</i>

42
00:03:58,503 --> 00:04:00,437
<i>A second Shuriken in his blind spot!</i>

43
00:04:09,281 --> 00:04:10,077
But...

44
00:04:11,850 --> 00:04:13,545
Still too naive.

45
00:04:14,953 --> 00:04:16,045
<i>He dodged it!</i>

46
00:04:28,433 --> 00:04:30,560
Here it is!

47
00:04:30,736 --> 00:04:35,730
<i>Kakashi. Sharingan Warrior!</i>

48
00:05:03,435 --> 00:05:05,027
You little brat!

49
00:05:20,986 --> 00:05:22,283
Kakashi Sensei!

50
00:05:28,493 --> 00:05:29,255
Naruto...

51
00:05:30,195 --> 00:05:31,958
Your strategy was outstanding.

52
00:05:33,065 --> 00:05:35,533
You've grown up...
Both of you.

53
00:05:37,636 --> 00:05:41,538
The purpose of the Shadow Clones
was not to take down Zabuza,

54
00:05:41,773 --> 00:05:46,506
but to hide my transformation
into Demon Wind Shuriken!

55
00:06:02,461 --> 00:06:06,591
I left one clone behind, then
transformed into Demon Wind Shuriken.

56
00:06:19,277 --> 00:06:22,576
Then a clone threw the real me, who had
transformed into Demon Wind Shuriken,

57
00:06:22,647 --> 00:06:23,614
towards Sasuke!

58
00:06:24,416 --> 00:06:25,474
<i>Sasuke!</i>

59
00:06:29,020 --> 00:06:30,248
When Sasuke got me,

60
00:06:30,322 --> 00:06:32,187
he must have realized
right away who I was.

61
00:06:32,724 --> 00:06:34,521
Then he took out his own Shuriken...

62
00:06:34,593 --> 00:06:36,652
And that's the Shadow Shuriken Jutsu!

63
00:06:45,170 --> 00:06:46,467
<i>Demon Wind Shuriken...</i>

64
00:06:47,139 --> 00:06:48,231
<i>Windmill of Shadows!</i>

65
00:06:51,143 --> 00:06:55,273
Hidden in the shadow of the real Shuriken,
I aimed for Zabuza.

66
00:06:55,881 --> 00:06:59,749
Of course I didn't think
I would defeat Zabuza!

67
00:07:00,252 --> 00:07:02,652
But I thought I'd destroy
the Water Prison.

68
00:07:03,188 --> 00:07:05,156
And as a bonus
I defeated his water clone, too...

69
00:07:05,891 --> 00:07:07,654
It was a huge success!

70
00:07:08,493 --> 00:07:09,926
That was a fluke...

71
00:07:10,529 --> 00:07:12,360
It was a fluke, huh!

72
00:07:13,198 --> 00:07:16,395
<i>Still, they performed oustandingly</i>
<i>in tandem...</i>

73
00:07:16,468 --> 00:07:17,867
<i>in this desperate situation.</i>

74
00:07:19,371 --> 00:07:20,463
<i>Despite the fact...</i>

75
00:07:20,739 --> 00:07:22,536
<i>that those two always</i>
<i>fight like cats and dogs.</i>

76
00:07:23,708 --> 00:07:24,367
Hmph...

77
00:07:24,476 --> 00:07:27,604
I got distracted and
broke my Water Prison Jutsu...

78
00:07:28,113 --> 00:07:29,045
That's not it!

79
00:07:29,748 --> 00:07:31,340
<i>You</i> didn't break the Jutsu...

80
00:07:32,684 --> 00:07:33,878
They <i>forced</i> you to break it.

81
00:07:42,227 --> 00:07:46,493
I'll tell you now,
the same Jutsu won't work on me twice.

82
00:07:47,599 --> 00:07:48,930
So what will you do?

83
00:08:00,612 --> 00:08:02,079
Sakura!
Stay alert.

84
00:08:38,617 --> 00:08:39,641
Sharingan!

85
00:08:41,253 --> 00:08:43,778
<i>Ushi, saru, u.</i>
<i>Ne, inoshishi, tori, ushi.</i>

86
00:08:43,889 --> 00:08:47,154
<i>Uma, tori, ne, tora.</i>
<i>Inu, tora, mi, ushi, hitsuji.</i>

87
00:08:47,225 --> 00:08:48,692
<i>Mi, inoshishi, hitsuji ne...</i>

88
00:08:50,128 --> 00:08:52,562
Ushi, saru, u.
Ne, inoshishi, tori, ushi.

89
00:08:52,731 --> 00:08:55,723
Uma, tori, ne, tora.
Inu, tora, mi, ushi, hitsuji.

90
00:08:55,901 --> 00:08:57,425
Mi, inoshishi, hitsuji ne.

91
00:08:59,104 --> 00:09:01,800
<i>Jin, saru, tori, tatsu.</i>
<i>Tori, ushi, uma, hitsuji.</i>

92
00:09:01,873 --> 00:09:04,273
<i>Tora, mi, ne, saru.</i>
<i>U, inoshishi, tatsu, hitsuji.</i>

93
00:09:04,409 --> 00:09:07,606
- <i>Ne, ushi, saru, tori. Jin, ne, inoshishi.</i>
- Jin, saru, tori, tatsu. Tori, ushi, uma, hitsuji.

94
00:09:07,679 --> 00:09:10,045
Tora, mi, ne, saru.
U, inoshishi, tatsu, hitsuji.

95
00:09:10,115 --> 00:09:12,242
Ne, ushi, saru, tori.
Jin, ne, inoshishi.

96
00:09:12,517 --> 00:09:13,040
Tori!

97
00:09:17,656 --> 00:09:19,419
Water Style!
Water Dragon Jutsu!

98
00:09:51,022 --> 00:09:53,047
<i>He copied that chant</i>
<i>in seconds...</i>

99
00:09:54,059 --> 00:09:55,822
<i>and so perfectly...!</i>

100
00:09:57,562 --> 00:09:59,325
<i>W-What is this?</i>

101
00:09:59,397 --> 00:10:00,386
<i>Is it Ninjutsu!</i>

102
00:10:18,616 --> 00:10:19,742
<i>Strange...</i>

103
00:10:20,118 --> 00:10:21,449
<i>What is going on...?</i>

104
00:10:22,921 --> 00:10:25,321
<i>Jin, saru, tori, tatsu.</i>
<i>Tori, ushi, uma, hitsuji.</i>

105
00:10:25,390 --> 00:10:27,221
<i>Tora, mi, ne, saru.</i>
<i>U, inoshishi, tatsu, hitsuji.</i>

106
00:10:27,292 --> 00:10:31,388
<i>The Sharingan is the ability to memorize</i>
<i>and copy the enemy's Jutsu...</i>

107
00:10:32,330 --> 00:10:33,194
<i>But...</i>

108
00:10:33,832 --> 00:10:34,764
<i>Tori!</i>

109
00:10:38,803 --> 00:10:40,703
<i>Water Style!</i>
<i>Water Dragon Jutsu!</i>

110
00:10:41,806 --> 00:10:44,274
<i>The Jutsu was set in motion</i>
<i>at the same time!</i>

111
00:10:45,877 --> 00:10:47,640
<i>By any chance, is this guy...</i>

112
00:11:11,137 --> 00:11:12,331
<i>This guy...!</i>

113
00:11:35,794 --> 00:11:37,318
The same identical movement!

114
00:11:38,097 --> 00:11:40,258
Furthermore, at exactly
the same time!

115
00:11:42,134 --> 00:11:43,863
What's going on, Sasuke!

116
00:11:51,243 --> 00:11:52,369
<i>This guy...</i>

117
00:11:53,312 --> 00:11:54,939
<i>My movements...!</i>

118
00:11:56,182 --> 00:11:57,706
<i>He's perfectly...</i>

119
00:11:58,751 --> 00:12:00,412
Reading them.

120
00:12:01,086 --> 00:12:02,053
<i>What?</i>

121
00:12:02,321 --> 00:12:04,812
<i>He's reading my mind?!</i>

122
00:12:09,395 --> 00:12:11,625
<i>Blast him! He's...</i>

123
00:12:12,298 --> 00:12:15,631
giving me
that barren, evil eye... right?

124
00:12:19,371 --> 00:12:23,740
Hah! You're just copying...
You're a pale imitation.

125
00:12:24,143 --> 00:12:26,577
- You won't be able to beat me!
- <i>You won't be able to beat me!</i>

126
00:12:26,779 --> 00:12:27,677
- You!
- <i>You!</i>

127
00:12:28,847 --> 00:12:32,840
I'll shut that copycat
monkey mouth permamently!

128
00:12:37,690 --> 00:12:38,952
<i>W-What's that!</i>

129
00:12:45,698 --> 00:12:46,528
<i>Me?</i>

130
00:12:47,433 --> 00:12:49,128
<i>R-Ridiculous!</i>

131
00:12:50,302 --> 00:12:52,099
<i>Is that his Genjutsu (lllusion Jutsu)?</i>

132
00:12:55,241 --> 00:12:57,641
Water Style!
Giant Vortex Jutsu!

133
00:13:05,317 --> 00:13:06,614
W-Wha!

134
00:13:12,324 --> 00:13:13,222
No way!

135
00:13:21,500 --> 00:13:24,162
<i>I was just about to</i>
<i>set forth that Jutsu...</i>

136
00:13:29,675 --> 00:13:31,233
<i>I can't keep up with...</i>

137
00:13:31,543 --> 00:13:32,805
<i>his Jutsu!</i>

138
00:14:23,629 --> 00:14:24,596
It's over...

139
00:14:43,215 --> 00:14:44,147
Why...?

140
00:14:45,184 --> 00:14:48,847
Are you able to see into the future...?

141
00:14:50,022 --> 00:14:50,647
Yeah...

142
00:14:52,257 --> 00:14:53,690
You're going to die!

143
00:15:19,251 --> 00:15:21,515
You were right. He died.

144
00:16:07,566 --> 00:16:09,261
He's definitely dead.

145
00:16:14,506 --> 00:16:15,666
I thank you.

146
00:16:16,809 --> 00:16:21,906
I have been waiting for the chance
to kill Zabuza.

147
00:16:25,317 --> 00:16:26,978
By the looks of that mask...

148
00:16:27,553 --> 00:16:30,215
You're a Tracker Ninja from
the Village Hidden in the Mist.

149
00:16:31,857 --> 00:16:34,724
Impressive. You're very knowledgeable.

150
00:16:36,261 --> 00:16:37,193
Tracker Ninja?

151
00:16:37,362 --> 00:16:39,296
You don't know what
a Tracker Ninja is?

152
00:16:39,898 --> 00:16:41,661
We learned it at
the Academy, didn't we?

153
00:16:42,267 --> 00:16:43,791
Tracker Ninja pursue...

154
00:16:44,369 --> 00:16:49,306
guys like Zabuza who turn against
the village where they were born and raised.

155
00:16:49,374 --> 00:16:51,934
And when they break away from
the village,

156
00:16:52,344 --> 00:16:54,073
Tracker Ninja go after these Rogue Ninja
and assassinate them...

157
00:16:54,746 --> 00:16:57,010
in order to avoid having
the secrets of the village being leaked.

158
00:16:58,350 --> 00:16:59,578
That's common knowledge!

159
00:16:59,952 --> 00:17:01,317
You should study more!

160
00:17:03,388 --> 00:17:04,150
That's right.

161
00:17:04,389 --> 00:17:06,880
I'm a member of Hidden Mist Village's
Tracking Unit

162
00:17:07,159 --> 00:17:09,320
whose mission is to
hunt Rogue Ninja.

163
00:17:10,496 --> 00:17:15,229
<i>From his height and voice,</i>
<i>he's not all that different from Naruto...</i>

164
00:17:16,401 --> 00:17:17,629
<i>A Tracker Ninja...?</i>

165
00:17:25,410 --> 00:17:28,277
<i>He's not just an ordinary kid...</i>

166
00:17:56,308 --> 00:17:58,833
What <i>are</i> you?!

167
00:18:06,919 --> 00:18:08,147
Hey you!

168
00:18:09,521 --> 00:18:12,513
Don't worry, Naruto.
He's not an enemy.

169
00:18:13,492 --> 00:18:15,585
That's not what I'm asking!

170
00:18:15,861 --> 00:18:16,919
I...!

171
00:18:17,563 --> 00:18:18,894
I mean!

172
00:18:19,097 --> 00:18:21,327
That Zabuza...
That Zabuza was killed!

173
00:18:22,034 --> 00:18:24,730
That guy who was so strong...

174
00:18:24,903 --> 00:18:28,862
He was killed so easily... by a kid
who's no different from me!

175
00:18:29,141 --> 00:18:30,369
We're...

176
00:18:30,642 --> 00:18:32,542
We're pathetic!

177
00:18:35,514 --> 00:18:37,345
I can't accept that!

178
00:18:39,518 --> 00:18:40,143
Well!

179
00:18:40,352 --> 00:18:42,445
I understand your disbelief.

180
00:18:43,188 --> 00:18:45,850
But... this, too, is reality.

181
00:18:51,129 --> 00:18:54,428
In this world, there are kids
who are younger than you...

182
00:18:55,467 --> 00:18:57,367
<i>and</i> stronger than me.

183
00:19:19,091 --> 00:19:23,289
Your battle is over for now.

184
00:19:24,196 --> 00:19:27,131
I must get rid of this corpse...

185
00:19:28,000 --> 00:19:30,730
because it contains many secrets.

186
00:19:32,971 --> 00:19:35,132
Now then, please excuse me.

187
00:19:40,379 --> 00:19:41,277
He's disappeared!

188
00:19:49,655 --> 00:19:51,282
He's not here anymore.

189
00:19:56,428 --> 00:19:59,158
What was all this for?!

190
00:19:59,498 --> 00:20:02,934
What are we anyway?!

191
00:20:05,704 --> 00:20:06,671
Naruto...

192
00:20:08,707 --> 00:20:12,165
Darn it! Darn it! Darn it!
DARN it!

193
00:20:15,213 --> 00:20:17,408
Things like this happen
when you're a Ninja.

194
00:20:18,650 --> 00:20:20,845
If you're frustrated,
apply it next time!

195
00:20:27,392 --> 00:20:29,826
Our mission hasn't ended yet.

196
00:20:31,196 --> 00:20:33,596
We must take Mr. Tazuna home.

197
00:20:37,102 --> 00:20:39,263
So sorry, everyone!

198
00:20:39,604 --> 00:20:42,402
You can rest at my house!

199
00:20:43,141 --> 00:20:43,869
Okay!

200
00:20:44,176 --> 00:20:45,438
Let's perk up and go!

201
00:20:59,658 --> 00:21:00,488
W-What!

202
00:21:00,726 --> 00:21:01,784
What happened!

203
00:21:03,662 --> 00:21:04,686
Kakashi Sensei!

204
00:21:12,838 --> 00:21:14,738
Kakashi Sensei!

205
00:22:53,456 --> 00:22:55,947
What'll we do?!

206
00:22:56,092 --> 00:22:58,322
Kakashi Sensei has collapsed!

207
00:22:58,461 --> 00:23:01,919
Gato's henchmen are probably
gonna come and attack us again!

208
00:23:02,165 --> 00:23:04,531
Guess it means we've gotta
fight by ourselves.

209
00:23:04,934 --> 00:23:07,129
Who knows if this training will
make us stronger but,

210
00:23:07,370 --> 00:23:08,803
it's getting interesting!

211
00:23:09,272 --> 00:23:11,433
I'll definitely get stronger.

212
00:23:12,642 --> 00:23:14,439
Next time:
"The Forest of Chakra."

213
00:23:14,677 --> 00:23:17,373
I'm going to kick butt once again!
